      <div class="knowledge-text">
        I learned software developement during an intensive <span id="coding">coding bootcamp</span> as well as a <span id="coding">freelancer</span> thereafter. I gained deep knowledge in HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript ES2015, SQL, git, Rails, React, Reacht Native and Redux.
